## 📖 System Overview

### MSD Pipeline Flow

```
User YAML Configuration
  ↓
Validation (schemas/)
  ↓
ModelBuilder (pipeline/ModelBuilder.js)
  ├─> Style Resolution
  ├─> Template Detection
  └─> finalStyle Creation
  ↓
AdvancedRenderer (renderer/AdvancedRenderer.js)
  ├─> Delegates to Specialized Renderers
  ├─> Builds SVG Markup
  └─> Caches DOM Elements
  ↓
SystemsManager (pipeline/SystemsManager.js)
  ├─> Entity Change Listener
  ├─> Rules Engine Evaluation
  ├─> Incremental Update Orchestration
  └─> Fallback to Selective Re-render
  ↓
BaseOverlayUpdater (BaseOverlayUpdater.js)
  ├─> DataSource Change Detection
  ├─> Template Processing
  └─> Content Updates
```

### Update Systems

**Two parallel update systems:**

#### 1. Content Updates (BaseOverlayUpdater)
- **Trigger:** Entity state changes
- **Detection:** Overlays with template placeholders (`{field.path}`)
- **Action:** Process templates with new entity data
- **Update:** Change text content, not styles
- **Performance:** Very fast (DOM text update only)

#### 2. Style Updates (SystemsManager Incremental)
- **Trigger:** Entity state changes + matching rules
- **Detection:** Rules engine produces style patches
- **Action:** Merge patches into `overlay.finalStyle`, call renderer
- **Update:** Change colors, sizes, other style properties
- **Performance:** Fast (no full rebuild), smooth transitions
- **Fallback:** Selective re-render if incremental not available

### Renderer Capabilities

| Overlay Type | Content Updates | Style Updates (Incremental) |
|--------------|----------------|----------------------------|
| StatusGrid | ✅ Via templates | ✅ Phase 1 Complete |
| ApexCharts | ✅ Via templates | ✅ Phase 2 Complete |
| Text | ✅ Via templates | ⏳ Phase 5 Pending |
| Button | ✅ Via templates | ⏳ Phase 3 Pending |
| Line | ❌ N/A | ⏳ Phase 4 Pending |
| Sparkline | ✅ Via templates | ⏳ Future |
| HistoryBar | ✅ Via templates | ⏳ Future |

