## 📊 Quick Reference

### File Locations

```
src/
├── msd/
│   ├── pipeline/
│   │   ├── SystemsManager.js      # Incremental update orchestration
│   │   └── ModelBuilder.js        # Initial model building
│   ├── renderer/
│   │   ├── AdvancedRenderer.js    # Rendering orchestration
│   │   ├── StatusGridRenderer.js  # StatusGrid with incremental updates
│   │   ├── ApexChartsOverlayRenderer.js  # ApexCharts with incremental updates
│   │   ├── TextOverlayRenderer.js
│   │   └── LineOverlayRenderer.js
│   ├── charts/
│   │   └── ApexChartsAdapter.js   # CSS variable resolution
│   ├── validation/
│   │   └── schemas/               # Validation schemas
│   └── BaseOverlayUpdater.js      # Content update system
```

### Key Classes & Methods

**SystemsManager:**
- `_overlayRenderers` - Renderer registry Map
- `_applyIncrementalUpdates()` - Orchestrate incremental updates
- `_findOverlayById()` - Lookup overlay config
- `_findOverlayElement()` - Lookup DOM element

**Renderer Interface:**
- `static render()` - Initial markup generation
- `static supportsIncrementalUpdate()` - Declare capability
- `static updateIncremental()` - Perform style update
- `static update{Type}Data()` - Perform content update

**BaseOverlayUpdater:**
- `_registerUpdaters()` - Register overlay types
- `_hasTemplateContent()` - Detect templates
- `updateOverlaysForDataSourceChanges()` - Trigger content updates

